<L>__{exterior busy street day}
<A>__{drake emerges onto the sidewalk of a busy street, four lanes of rush hour traffic whizzing past. abruptly, drake cuts into the traffic, leaping atop the hood of an oncoming car. the car's horn sounds, brakes squeal.}
<D>__{blade follows, jumping onto the hood of another car. more horns sound.}
<A>__{in this manner. drake and blade race across the flowing traffic itself. using the hoods and roofs of the cars like moving stepping stones.}
